{"tid":466213,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"鐵達尼號(1997年電影)有三樣野一直好少人會討論","createTime":"2017-11-12T10:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T14:07:28.000Z","uid":120980,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4a78a32777e0b6cd3f37369099a7d697c060f908","tid":466213,"uid":120980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:29:33.000Z","msg":"第一:就算企船頭吹風係幾咁浪漫 就算Jack and Rose段愛情故事係幾咁刻骨銘心 <br />\n始終Jack先係著紅鞋 俾綠帽人地戴果個 <br />\n<br />\n第二:電影中鐵達尼撞冰山除咗因為人為錯誤之外 主要嘅理由似係因為瞭望台人員掛住昅人(男女主角)打茄輪先會導致延誤發現冰山兼響鐘通知 <br />\n<br />\n第三:個個人都淨係記得Jack讓塊木板俾Rose瞓住等救結果自己凍死 <br />\n但係又忽略咗Rose隔離含住哨子死咗果個人 Jack其實只係輔助 <br />\n查實Rose之所以救得翻 最大功勞都係果支哨子 唔係因為Rose有雞吹 隻艇根本唔會翻轉頭 Rose繼續冇力嗌 一樣係要等凍死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bab5a8a22bfa730822cfe86bd67c831f5f0797c","tid":466213,"uid":64404,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"咁有咩好討論?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b7ec1e29380f11a2cca946e010be7b5051ed9f","tid":466213,"uid":3747,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"捷克斯洛伐克"},{"pid":"0b2f11bfce227e669e19334ee4397360ed82371b","tid":466213,"uid":45352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"你呢幾樣野有咩討論價值"},{"pid":"4a246ae7d0e2b15fdc9f08f3e35ec5bcdbd3ed37","tid":466213,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:44:46.000Z","msg":"無人想知"},{"pid":"1c97e4b07082b14122903cc41a8a9b4a43d273e7","tid":466213,"uid":17268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"第三樣，無果塊木板，rose 一早凍死左，仲邊有力游去拎個哨子黎吹"},{"pid":"59322052afa11712cfa97e6c72ef836e754d802a","tid":466213,"uid":13946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:03:50.000Z","msg":"第二:<br />\n<br />\n即係你都排除咗人為錯誤，咁瞭望員掛住望人打茄輪係機械故障？"},{"pid":"04cb9d7feb42945a09587b10c8f128512e869720","tid":466213,"uid":13929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:06:36.000Z","msg":"咁你不如話rose夠肥先頂得住低溫<br />\n架艇仔都係輔助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎埋啲冇討論價值嘅嘢講"},{"pid":"61b937509f86d68aaf06e2456bf4a7d57e9cbda8","tid":466213,"uid":43159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:07:13.000Z","msg":"2同3完全無野可討論"},{"pid":"a770937e5a6a2d4970d13a000e8319de36e2992e","tid":466213,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:12:02.000Z","msg":"樓主好叻叻呀，睇得咁透徹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8cb1c99e120f5a50757fc0c3cca0f8ac3debca","tid":466213,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"第一錯<br />\n女主根本唔鍾意果條友<br />\n佢地根本冇一齊過冇拍拖，只係指腹為婚，得果條友鍾意女主<br />\n冇拍拖就冇帽，果條友係兵"},{"pid":"694a0f4d605aaf37817f56082ce226708d2682e1","tid":466213,"uid":63345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:36:53.000Z","msg":"樓主97諗到而家，點知一野俾人打沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9196208cee79fcc2e04cfe585ec21ce11854b1f7","tid":466213,"uid":25002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:45:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89c3a1536a171fae109908e4adff2bfd34f59293","tid":466213,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"其實隻船冇事到左舊金山，Jack同Rose會唔會有將來，仲有冇咁刻骨銘心既愛情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafef655db2d80e3df3a3335db962f10f90fc435","tid":466213,"uid":122434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捷克斯洛伐克</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab2f1351737812a500b4e67b2d98e1cb7247631","tid":466213,"uid":122434,"like":